Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8\fad(200,0)}本集字幕将从正片开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 你挡着我道了 ♪\N{\fnArial\fs18}♪ You're standing on my neck ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn叶根友行书繁\fs70\shad0\bord2\c&H061A18&\3c&H86BFB8&}拽妹Daria
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs22\shad1\c&H70D8FB&\fn迷你简汉真广标\b0\pos(312,420)}漫迪字幕组&@Daria拽妹黛薇儿\N\N——·@严肃活泼小kk译制·——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你搞坏我的蛋糕啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! You're ruining my birthday cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她搞砸的才不仅限于此\N{\fnArial\fs18}If only that were all she ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:00:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快让她住手\N{\fnArial\fs18}Make her stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 她只是个小宝宝\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Daria, she's just a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她也想玩嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}She wants to play, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是个萌宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm such a cute baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为毛我就不能是独生女?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why can't I be an only child?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说嘛 为毛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. Why can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在这亲眼见证自己的人生走向很美妙吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Isn't it great to sit here and see your whole life unfold before your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就和溺水一样妙不可言\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's almost as good as drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们 猜猜怎么着?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Girls, guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了一盒子我老爹给我童年拍的老家庭电影\N{\fnArial\fs18}I found a box of old home movies my dad took of me when I was a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它们转成录像带了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm having them transferred to video tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.57,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想我为嘛就从来没有过尴尬阶段呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wonder why I never went through an awkward phase?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让你看她出生?\N{\fnArial\fs18}He wanted you to watch her birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那能让你产生终生不可磨灭的创伤\N{\fnArial\fs18}That could scar you for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我出生就自带创伤\N{\fnArial\fs18}The birth itself did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,说到永久性的伤害...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Speaking of permanent damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我可看不到任何蔬菜哟\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't see any vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该从我这角度看看\N{\fnArial\fs18}You should have my view.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要蔬菜干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在食物大战中用来扔屏幕么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}To throw at the screen during the big food fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什么食物大战?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What food fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你是笨蛋不是?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, are you thick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是电影节的食物\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is the Food in Film Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你上个月没去看《洛基恐怖秀》吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Didn't you see the Rocky Horror Picture Show last month?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevin和我穿上了彼此的内衣裤\N{\fnArial\fs18}Kevin and I wore each other's underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:01:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,又穿了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真抱歉让你失望了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry to disappoint you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可我不觉得这很有意思\N{\fnArial\fs18}but I don't think this is an interactive event.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚他们要播《Andre Sakarynsky的最后晚餐》\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tonight they're showing Andre Sakarynsky's Last Meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,20世纪30年代的俄罗斯艺术电影\N{\fnArial\fs18}A Russian art film from the 1930s.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,俄罗斯?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Russian?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,字幕\N{\fnArial\fs18}Subtitles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.48,0:02:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你没碰巧保存了Kevin的什么创作吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You didn't happen to save any of Kevin's produce, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要被老师看到了\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're about to be seen with a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 O'Neill老师\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hi, Mr. O'Neill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 孩子们 我太受鼓舞了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hi, girls! I'm just so invigorated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好的电影院是永恒的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Great cinema is timeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,放在今天就拍不出那电影了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Couldn't that movie have been made today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜 要是你能找到人去发掘演员的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess, if you could find someone to exhume the actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我能送你俩回家么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can I give you two a lift home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不用客气 我们喜欢走路\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, that's okay. We love to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 今晚对于散长步来说最完美不过了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, it's a perfect night for a nice long stroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不坐到前面去么 Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you want to sit in the front, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想 可是\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'd love to, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 我怕会被气囊弄伤\N{\fnArial\fs18}you know, I'm afraid of an airbag injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,噢天啊 太抱歉了 我到底在想什么呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, my gosh, I'm so sorry, what was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然得坐到后座去\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course you must sit in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候我觉得电影比小说更像是我们生活的影射\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sometimes I think film is even more a mirror of our times than the novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这是不是因为它更逼真?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do you think this is because of its greater verisimilitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jane?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我在后面听不到你说话啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't really hear you back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,公路噪音太大\N{\fnArial\fs18}Road noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 我不知道逼真是啥意思\N{\fnArial\fs18}Plus, I don't know what verisimilitude means.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What about you, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,面对现实吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多数人宁愿看电影都不愿意看书\N{\fnArial\fs18}Most people would rather watch a movie than read a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看电影更省事更简单 而且你压根不用担心嘴唇要运动\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's fast, it's easy, and you don't have to worry about your lips moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一项极好的课堂作业 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}That is a fabulous class assignment, Daria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的提议\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thank you for the suggestion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我提什么议啦?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, did I make a suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要是提了的话 我恳请撤回\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because if so, I'd like to withdraw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以咧 作为现实文学的练习\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, as an exercise in living literature,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都要自己制作电影\N{\fnArial\fs18}you'll all be making your own movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得谢谢Daria给出如此振奋的提议\N{\fnArial\fs18}We have Daria to thank for that exciting suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,又是那个词\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's that word again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 在我们分电影小组前\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, before we split into movie making teams,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谁想当导演?\N{\fnArial\fs18}who would like to direct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,记住 这是个非常宝贵 精密 和非常非常贵的仪器\N{\fnArial\fs18}Remember, this is a precious, precise, and very, very costly instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是会随随便便借给青少年的东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not the sort of thing one ordinarily lends a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会小心的\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你解释过三种对焦模式啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I explained to you about the three focus modes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有归档覆盖以及自动睡眠功能\N{\fnArial\fs18}and the depth of field override and the auto-sleep feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己都快自动睡眠了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm about to go into auto-sleep myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 Daria 就是... 尽量不要用它就好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, Daria. Just... try not to use it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 树像头\N{\fnArial\fs18}There. Tree-Cam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这样把它开机扔在这?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're just going to leave it running?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就扔个一两天\N{\fnArial\fs18}Only a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,它会用树的客观视角来捕捉每一位路过的行人\N{\fnArial\fs18}It'll catch everyone passing by through the tree's totally objective point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,引人入胜\N{\fnArial\fs18}Riveting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}安迪·沃霍尔 波普艺术的倡导者和领袖\N此处指其电影《沉睡》(Sleep 1963) 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Andy Warhol拍了一个家伙睡8小时觉的片子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Andy Warhol filmed eight hours of a guy sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而大家都觉得那很棒\N{\fnArial\fs18}and people thought it was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,接触到12步疗法后那些人就改变了想法\N{\fnArial\fs18}Those people changed their minds after they got into twelve step programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,等等...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了树叶的摩擦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think I just saw some leaves rustle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们的高潮\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's our climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们需要一个剧本\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe we need a script.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你打开窗 说\N{\fnArial\fs18}And then you open the window and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"生活是无意义地堕入虚空\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Life is a meaningless descent into the void."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你跳下去 在坠落中尖叫\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then you jump, and on the way down you scream,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我可明白了 我什么都明白了"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Now I understand, I understand everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你能去掉窗户的那段 给我点有意思的台词么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can you get rid of the window part and give me something funny to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,再来只贵宾犬\N{\fnArial\fs18}And a poodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的超级想演我牵着贵宾犬散步耶\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'd really like to be in a scene where I'm walking a poodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真大牌\N{\fnArial\fs18}Actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"没有出路吗?"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Is there no way out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,此路不通 朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}"No exit, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩我们被关在这房间里 千秋万世"\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's just us, stuck in this room together, forever and ever."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}BY萨特 存在主义者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"救命 他人即地狱"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Help! Hell is other people."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,转念想想 自我即地狱\N{\fnArial\fs18}On second thought, hell is myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 宝贝 你得像有好几年没见到我一样跑向我\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, babe, you gotta run to me like you haven't seen me in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前在中国 记住了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I've been in China, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在做慢动作 就像Jodie说的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I was trying to do it in slow motion, like Jodie said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,慢动作镜头是后期加的 你这傻X\N{\fnArial\fs18}You add the slow motion part after, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在乎啊 这真恶心\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who cares. This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想拍超市罢工的电影\N{\fnArial\fs18}I really want to do a film about the supermarket strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可我都买了这套礼服 我穿这个可演不了收银员\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I already paid for this gown. I can't play a checkout girl in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是纪录片\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a documentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要礼服\N{\fnArial\fs18}You don't need the gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,噢不 我才不要拍裸露片\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, no! I won't do a nude scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你说是角色特性的需要\N{\fnArial\fs18}Unless you think it's crucial to my character.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我能借你的衣服出席今晚的时尚俱乐部派对么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can I borrow something to wear to the Fashion Club party tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快检查她脑子是不是撞傻了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Check her head for bumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托啦 Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Please, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是潮流禁穿晚会\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's the Fashion Don'ts Costume Gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 一个潮流禁穿晚会可以是一种... 电影素材\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, a Fashion Don'ts Costume Party could be kind of... cinematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 告诉你怎么着 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. I'll tell you what,Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你借我的衣服\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll lend you an outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但你今晚得让我拍摄你和你的朋友\N{\fnArial\fs18}but you have to let me videotape you and your friends tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什么玩意 照相机么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What, like, with a camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对 要拍电影 课堂作业\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes. For a movie, for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么会会拒绝你呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why would I say no to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她有奇异的吸引力\N{\fnArial\fs18}She's strangely mesmerizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,肤浅... 自恋... 自以为是...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Superficial... narcissistic... self-absorbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她有明星气质 搞定\N{\fnArial\fs18}she's got star quality, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你的禁穿打扮 Sandi\N{\fnArial\fs18}I love your don'ts, Sandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可瞧瞧你 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}But look at you, Quinn:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,方领上衣 下装太长 还配错鞋子\N{\fnArial\fs18}boxy top with too long bottom and the wrong shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在哪搞来这套装扮?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Where did you ever come up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你真是天才\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, you're a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我嘛 我就像艺术家 这就是姐表达自我的方式\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm, like, an artist, and this is how I express myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 颜色真丑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh! Bad color!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她比录像带上还吓人\N{\fnArial\fs18}She's even scarier on tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这派对只是冰山一角\N{\fnArial\fs18}This party is just the tip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发掘到了主题\N{\fnArial\fs18}We've found our subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说...\N{\fnArial\fs18}You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn Morgendorffer的一天\N{\fnArial\fs18}A day in the life of Quinn Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你想拍恐怖片?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you sure you want to do a horror movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们要一整天都跟着我\N{\fnArial\fs18}So they're going to follow me around for a whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,或者一分钟 取决于我们能忍受多久\N{\fnArial\fs18}Or a minute, depending on how much we can stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能早早回家并有机会做晚饭真是好极了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's so nice to get home early and have a chance to make dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你确定你要这么做?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, are you sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你的隐私怎么办?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What about your privacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家的人什么时候变得这么害怕隐私外泄啦?\N{\fnArial\fs18}When did this family turn into such a bunch of privacy freaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哥的录像来喽\N{\fnArial\fs18}My video transfers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真是迫不及待要重回童年啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't wait to relive my childhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃完饭来看带子么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Shall we watch after dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我得在播映前写点小故事\N{\fnArial\fs18}I thought I'd write a little narration before the big screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想抓住这个时期的本质\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want to capture the whole essence of the period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不记得你对这些日子有讨喜的记忆\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't remember you having such fond memories of those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我全都想起来了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's all coming back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,它真让人怀念童年\N{\fnArial\fs18}It really makes you feel nostalgic for your childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的黄金时刻\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is your golden time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,享受青春 女孩们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Enjoy your youth, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不吃甜点了 我不想明天看起来胖胖的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think I'll pass on dessert. I don't want to look puffy tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜我就自个儿去看会电视吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess I'll go watch TV by myself for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,当这些芭蕾舞者能在酒吧混得开 她们就能在酒吧混得开\N{\fnArial\fs18}When these ballerinas work out at the bar, they work out at the bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,呕心小世界即将为您播映《喝醉的芭蕾舞裙》\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tanked in a tutu when Sick, Sad World returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 我在想你能不能告诉我你对Quinn这部电影的想法?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, I wonder if you'd tell me what you have in mind for this movie of Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只是英语课要求的一项蹩脚作业而已\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's just a lame assignment for English class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 干嘛要拍Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, why Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她有活力又上镜\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, she's lively, she's photogenic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜嘛? 她很活泼\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know what? She's bubbly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得一天都对Quinn进行跟踪拍摄\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're going to follow around Quinn for a day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,并向世人展示有魅力又受欢迎是怎么一回事\N{\fnArial\fs18}and show the world what it's like to be attractive and popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人对那就很好奇\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm kind of curious about that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只是有时候\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's just that sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你按很严格的标准去评价别人的行为\N{\fnArial\fs18}you judge people's behavior by a pretty rigid set of standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不是每个人都能按那一套生活\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not everyone can live up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是这个世界的错误之处\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's what's wrong with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至你自己也不是时刻遵守着那套\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not even you live up to them all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜我能对她放宽点\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess I could go easy on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 亲爱的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不过不要惊讶哟\N{\fnArial\fs18}But don't hold your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,放手大干吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Rarin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,记住 我们在揭露一个虚伪 以自我为中心的自大狂\N{\fnArial\fs18}Remember, we're exposing a hollow, self-centered egomaniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 我们不需要太费劲\N{\fnArial\fs18}Trust me. We won't have to work very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就说早晨不是她的黄金时刻好啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's just say mornings are not her best time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好呀 美丽的世界\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good morning, beautiful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是要拍我吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you want to shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我是要拍你\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes. I want to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 话说我哪边脸比较好看?\N{\fnArial\fs18}By the way, which is my best side?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道两边都很美\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know they're both good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你都已经化好妆了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're already wearing makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\fnArial\fs18}I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是碰巧天生丽质 素颜就美\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just happen to be the kind of person who doesn't really need makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那你化妆是因为...\N{\fnArial\fs18}So you're putting it on because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不是每个人都像我一样幸运\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not everyone is as lucky as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我想成为所有人的榜样\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want to be a role model for all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至是那些急需化妆的人\N{\fnArial\fs18}Even the ones who need makeup really badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我得坐下来 我有点晕了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think I need to sit down. I'm getting dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,人们 团结一致 永不分离\N{\fnArial\fs18}The people, united, will never be divided!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都站在那干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why are they all standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有管理纠纷 所以罢工了\N{\fnArial\fs18}They're having a dispute with management, so they refuse to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,得有人告诉他们 他们占用人行道了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Someone should tell them they're taking up the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我您为什么罢工 您希望这能达到什么目的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tell me why you're on strike and what you hope to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再简单不过了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's simple enough:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有劳有得\N{\fnArial\fs18}an honest day's pay for an honest day's work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,停止剥削我们的利益\N{\fnArial\fs18}and stop chiseling away at our benefits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我有东西想要 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm getting a craving, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力小蛋糕吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ho-Hos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs18}No problem, babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 打扰啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! Escuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,力量瑜伽是一项很好的运动\N{\fnArial\fs18}Power yoga is a really good thing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为内在美和外在美同样重要\N{\fnArial\fs18}because inner beauty is just as important as outer beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就像 你能光有CD没有CD播放器么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Like, can you have a CD without a CD player?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不这么认为\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是纯真的年代\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was a time of innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那个年代你不用锁门 一颗糖才卖五美分\N{\fnArial\fs18}when you left your doors unlocked and candy bars cost a nickel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然两件事没关系 我...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not that those two facts are related, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 让我从这开始\N{\fnArial\fs18}aww, dammit! Lemme start over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一段无忧无虑的时光\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was a carefree time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小男孩能在阳光照耀的大街上学骑单车\N{\fnArial\fs18}when a young boy could learn to ride a bike on sun-dappled streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 为什么没有人帮帮那可怜的小孩?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! Hey! Why doesn't anybody help that poor kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他擦伤了膝盖 噢我懂了\N{\fnArial\fs18}He skinned his knee! Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"坐回单车上去 Jake 男子汉才不哭鼻子\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Get back on the bike Jake. Big boys don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩子才哭鼻子 Jakey"\N{\fnArial\fs18}Crying is for girls, Jakey."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,摇摇晃晃 歪歪倒倒\N{\fnArial\fs18}Shake, shake, quiver and quake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在可都想起来了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's all coming back to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我们去哪 你表姐和她小伙伴是不是得一直跟着?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are your cousin and her friend going to follow us everywhere we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不是和你说了嘛 无视他们就好\N{\fnArial\fs18}I told you, just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是这么说 可他们不是总是都拿着相机喽\N{\fnArial\fs18}You always say that about them, but they don't usually have a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我参与的一项小研究 噢 强迫参与\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's a little project that I got, um, forced into.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 你觉得我哪边脸更美?\N{\fnArial\fs18}By the way, which do you think is my best side?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,都很美\N{\fnArial\fs18}They're both good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,人家造啦 不过这边脸的酒窝更可爱耶\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know, but this side has my better dimples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我还能忍多久\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't know how much more of this I can take.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,亲?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你能去看看他们有没有不放芝士的披萨么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Would you find out if they have those cheeseless pizzas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 噢 他是 Zachary\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Sure! - And, uh, it's Zachary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛邀请他一块来呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why did you invite that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你这周是和Larry交往\N{\fnArial\fs18}I thought you were going steady with Larry this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Larry的车废了 Zachary能开他老妈的车\N{\fnArial\fs18}Larry totaled his car. Zachary's got his mom's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真聪明 Quinn 你总是能未雨绸缪\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're so smart, Quinn. You always think ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:12:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了么 听到了么 亲们?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did you hear that? Did you hear that, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,亲们?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 看那可爱的小男孩\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, look at that cute little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他长成了一个如此英俊的男子\N{\fnArial\fs18}And he grew up into such a handsome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你要开点灯吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Honey? Wouldn't you like a little more light in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 Jake 我去厨房赶我的文书工作\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, Jake, I'm just going to catch up on some paperwork in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你送我们来 Aaron\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks for driving us here, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Zachary.\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's Zachary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这么说\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可是购物是女孩子的事儿\N{\fnArial\fs18}But shopping is kind of a girl thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你能待会再来找我们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe you could meet us after or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那我这期间要做什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But what will I do in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不造耶 你有什么要买的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't know. Do you have any shopping to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你想给什么特别的人买份礼物?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe there's someone special you want to get a present for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你就很特别 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, well, you're kind of special, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 Zachary 你不用给人家买礼物了啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Zachary, you don't have to get me a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你去Junior 5店找Theresa 说你是给Quinn买的\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you ask for Theresa in Junior 5 and tell her it's for Quinn,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她就会帮你搞定\N{\fnArial\fs18}she'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你拍到没? 我希望你拍到了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did you get that? I hope you got that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你造"毛孔收敛"倒过来拼是"雷利法吸虫"吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did you know that "pore refiner" spelt backwards is "renifer erop"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,把那给我\N{\fnArial\fs18}Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 看呀 收缩水\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, look! Pore refiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我真高兴我用不着那个\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm glad I don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有意识到为毛受欢迎的人的毛孔都很小?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Have you ever noticed how popular people always have the tiniest pores?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这又是为毛呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wonder why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你的毛孔都很可爱 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your pores are very cute, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可你看不到它们呀 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But you can't seem them, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,噢天啊 他们在... 他们在对焦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, my God, they've been... they've been zooming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好不要拉近 别再对焦了 我说真的\N{\fnArial\fs18}You better not zoom that thing. Stop zooming, I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在镜头上能看到我的任何一个毛孔 我发誓 我要宰了你\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you can see any of my pores on camera, I swear, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别拍了 我才没有毛孔\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stop the tape! I do not have pores!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的毛孔都很可爱 我的毛孔超小的\N{\fnArial\fs18}My pores are cute! My pores are tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你被炒啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你说什么都会被用来对付你\N{\fnArial\fs18}Anything you say can and will be used against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拍好啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}We've got our Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,杀青喽\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's a wrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但是包臀裙绝对是时尚禁止\N{\fnArial\fs18}But a wrap is a definite don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天哟 这话真的是从我嘴里蹦出来的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, my God. Did I really just say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我有最可爱最细致的毛孔啦 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I have the cutest little pores, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦 每一个都像是小酒窝\N{\fnArial\fs18}You really do. Each one is like a tiny dimple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我也能有你的毛孔 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wish I had pores like yours, Daria
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"像你的毛孔"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Pores Like Yours."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那对于毛孔调理磨砂膏来说真是好名字\N{\fnArial\fs18}That would be a great name for a pore conditioning exfoliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,天呀 Daria 你是怎么做到的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}God, Daria, how do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在恭维你的完美毛孔\N{\fnArial\fs18}Here we are, complimenting you on your perfect pores,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却慈悲为怀地思考自己能怎么去改善他人的毛孔\N{\fnArial\fs18}and you're unselfishly thinking about how you can improve the pores of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}pores与pours同音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是下雨啦 就想到倾盆了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Duh! I guess when it rains, it "pores."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 你在干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dad? What are you doing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一个小宝宝 我需要照顾\N{\fnArial\fs18}I was a child. I needed attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的膝盖受过轻伤\N{\fnArial\fs18}I had a boo-boo on my knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可是大体是痊愈了吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, it's pretty much healed now, though. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在乎么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did anyone care?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有人在乎呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}No one cared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我从未有过的 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is what I never had, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在是这样做: 简单的亲子联系\N{\fnArial\fs18}What we're doing now: simple parent/child bonding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你妈费了多大劲才让我们这样亲近\N{\fnArial\fs18}The kind of closeness your mother and I have worked so hard to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,天 真搞笑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Gee, that's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我都能发誓我是从梦中醒来\N{\fnArial\fs18}I could've sworn I woke up from the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你可不能给这样的时刻定价 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}You just can't put a price on a moment like this, Daria,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而且一旦这些日子远去 它们就是远去了\N{\fnArial\fs18}and once these years are gone, they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,爸 都四点了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dad, it's 4:00 A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才最可怕的噩梦醒来: 模仿我妹\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just woke up from my worst nightmare: resembling my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你则在重温40年前的父母的疏忽照顾\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're reliving an instance of parental neglect from forty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你把这叫做亲子联系?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You call this parent/child bonding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说是\N{\fnArial\fs18}Works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再看一遍吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's watch again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你来这碰头\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks for meeting me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来你昨晚过得不咋地啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Looks like you had a rough night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,答应我如果我开始言行举止或者思考都和Quinn一样\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just promise me that if I start acting, talking, or thinking like Quinn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做正确的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}you'll do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要是药物治疗没效果 我会授权电击\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you don't respond to drug therapy, I'll authorize electric shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,噢对了 你的小毛孔儿今天很萌噢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, and by the way, your teensy-weensy pores look really cute today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可我哪边脸比较美?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But which is my best side, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我造都很美啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know they're both good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是忘了说是谁送我来的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did I forget to mention who drove me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要是在镜头上能看到我的任何一个毛孔 我发誓 我要宰了你\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you can see any of my pores on camera, I swear, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,别拍啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stop the tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这太简单了\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,易如反掌\N{\fnArial\fs18}Shooting ducks in a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,电影拍得咋样了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How's that film project coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,自从你妹妹在她独舞汇演上摔倒 我都没见过你那么开心\N{\fnArial\fs18}I haven't seen you so amused since your sister fell at her dance recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是我摔倒了\N{\fnArial\fs18}That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是你们其中一个嘲笑另外一个啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I knew it was one of you girls laughing at one of you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能偷看一眼么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can I sneak a peek?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在编辑\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're still editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn很有银幕表现力\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn's got a real screen presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我哪边脸比较美?\N{\fnArial\fs18}By the way, which is my best side?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我造两边都很美啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know they're both good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你能在镜头上看到我的任何一个毛孔 我发誓 我要宰了你\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you can see any of my pores on camera, I swear, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别拍啦 我才没有毛孔\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stop the tape! I do not have pores!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的毛孔很可爱 我的毛孔超小的\N{\fnArial\fs18}My pores are cute! My pores are tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你被炒啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 这有点残酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, my. This is a little cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定你没把她说的话断章取义?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you sure you haven't taken her out of context?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她自创的语句\N{\fnArial\fs18}She creates her own context.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你造吗 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, Daria,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让Quinn拍一部显得她姐姐很滑稽的电影\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wouldn't let Quinn make a movie that made her sister look ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么会嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How could she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她压根不承认她已经拍了\N{\fnArial\fs18}She doesn't admit to having one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你怎么着 Daria 你爱咋咋地\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll tell you what, Daria: you do what you think is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢那话\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 她显然高估了我的感受\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't worry. She's clearly overestimated my conscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还假设我有感受\N{\fnArial\fs18}by assuming I have one at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我哪边脸比较美?\N{\fnArial\fs18}By the way, which is my best side?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的电影吗? 我能看吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is that my movie? Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 可那会扰乱创意工程\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry, but that would interfere with the creative process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 我们就像演员 这就是我们怎么表达自我\N{\fnArial\fs18}See, we're like artists, and this is how we express ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的\N{\fnArial\fs18}You understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我迫不及待要看啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't wait to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望自己说的话不会很蠢\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just hope I don't sound stupid or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,人家本来就不会\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not that I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,打消念头\N{\fnArial\fs18}Perish the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是 我造有时候有部分人\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just, I know that sometimes certain types of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嫉妒心很强的人 会认为 她以为她谁呀?\N{\fnArial\fs18}jealous people, might think, who does she think she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我有时候就会这样想\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because I sometimes think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可我不允许自己这样想太久\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I can't let myself go on too long thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,或是别的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 有时候我和Sandi Stacy还有Tiffany一起走下大厅\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, sometimes I'm walking down the hall with Sandi, Stacy, and Tiffany,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我突然就脱离了自我 旁观着 就好像\N{\fnArial\fs18}and suddenly I'm outside of myself, watching, and it's, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"这些女的是谁?\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Who are these girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她们除了男人 衣服 车子 就没别的可聊了么?"\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can't they talk about anything but guys, and clothes, and cars?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可然后呢 我们还能聊什么嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But then, what would we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你得擅长做某件事\N{\fnArial\fs18}You have to be good at something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你读写什么的都很厉害\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're good at your reading and writing and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而你画画也很强\N{\fnArial\fs18}and you're good at your little paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可这些微不足道吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}They are miniscule, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我发觉 有魅力又受欢迎 就是我擅长的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}I figure, being attractive and popular, that's what I'm good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这不是那么重要了啦 不过你懂嘛 这就是我擅长的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe it's not that important, but, you know, it's what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,作孽\N{\fnArial\fs18}Aw, hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Jodie 你是从哪学到欺骗象征手法的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jodie, where did you learn to juggle symbolism like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我用了情节串联图板 我猜那有帮助吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, I worked with storyboards. I think that helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来 Daria和Jane的作品\N{\fnArial\fs18}And now, a work by Daria and Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我想成为所有人的榜样\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want to be a role model for all people,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至是那些急需化妆的人\N{\fnArial\fs18}even the ones that need makeup really badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我哪边脸比较美?\N{\fnArial\fs18}By the way, which is my best side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像 你能光有CD没有CD播放器么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Like, can you have a CD without a CD player?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不这么认为\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我哪边脸比较美?\N{\fnArial\fs18}By the way, which is my best side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,别弄得好像你化了浓妆\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't look like you have on too much makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,化裸妆让你看起来像没怎么化\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wear enough to make it look like you don't have much on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我哪边脸比较美?\N{\fnArial\fs18}By the way, which is my best side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fnArial\fs18}Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你和我分享我的一天\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks for sharing my day with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,记住 时尚代表着趣味\N{\fnArial\fs18}And remember, fashion is fun and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们得身体力行地为雨林做点事\N{\fnArial\fs18}but we should really do something about the rainforest and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么玩意?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我和她说我再给她个机会\N{\fnArial\fs18}I told her I'd give her the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,去展示自己的内心并不肤浅\N{\fnArial\fs18}to show there was more to her than the surface Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,结果发现她还是没变\N{\fnArial\fs18}Turns out there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那毛孔那段到底去哪了? 我们最终完工的呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And what exactly happened to the pore stuff? Our big finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你造那个我没有的感受吧 我有了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know the conscious I don't have? It got to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,肤浅的深度 的确很刺激\N{\fnArial\fs18}The Depths of Shallowness. Provocative indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 如果我们...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, what if we...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们 你俩的电影确实屌炸天\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your movie really kicked butt, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那是\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我说真的 它真有捕捉到一种绝望\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean it! It really captured a kind of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹让我好悲伤\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your sister makes me so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fnArial\fs18}You and me both.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你是那个电影女孩 我爱你\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're the girl from the movie! I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪边脸比较美? 你能告诉我吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Which is my best side? Can you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我才真是悲伤\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now I'm really sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,天哟 我以为我是唯一一个为毛孔耻辱的人\N{\fnArial\fs18}God, I thought I was the only one ashamed of my pores.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都耻辱毛孔 可你不能耻辱自己的耻辱\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're all ashamed of our pores, but you mustn't be ashamed of your shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 你好心做坏事啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, you did the compassionate thing, and look where it got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她比以前更受欢迎了\N{\fnArial\fs18}She's more popular than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们着手做揭露 结果成情书\N{\fnArial\fs18}We set out to make an exposé, it ends up a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧见没 我们就像艺术家 这就是我们如何表达自我\N{\fnArial\fs18}See, we're like artists, and this is how we screw ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,至于你 你也能拥有富有弹性的秀发\N{\fnArial\fs18}And you, too, can have bouncy hair
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有时间把它从里往外卷\N{\fnArial\fs18}if you just take the time to bounce from the inside as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 大家 和我一起弹起来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, everyone! Bounce with me!
